data.description: Seller offering $1500 carpet allowance. Brand new roof installed! Opportunity awaits in the desirable Columbine Hills community in Littleton. Enjoy being minutes away to Chatfield State Park full of incredible outdoor amenities, such as boating, nature trails to explore, camping and picnics. Located on a pretty tree-lined street on an oversized premium lot with great curb appeal. Inside, find a spacious layout enhanced with both formal and informal living spaces, 8 panel doors, great natural light, cozy wood-burning fireplace, neutral color palette, finished basement – and so much more! Incredible oversized private backyard with a secluded fenced in deck, separate patio, garden areas, spacious yard ready to play, and plenty of mature trees and shrubbery to provide a serene atmosphere great for relaxation. Backyard shed with electrical makes a great studio or he/she cave. 2-car attached garage with ample off street parking perfect for an RV or boat. Convenience is key in this location, with easy access Columbine Hills community park, shops, restaurants, and major highways to get anywhere you need quickly.
